<!-- ── OPENER ──────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="opener section">
  <p>Somewhere in the Middle East, history is being rewritten in smoke and fire.</p>
  <p>Somewhere in India, your LPG cylinder is quietly testing both your patience and your budget.</p>
